  • Golden Strap

From the highly popular and prominent watchmakers Sonata comes this ultra-elegant women’s watch that belongs to the Sona Sitara range of designer timepieces. As an ideal choice of personal timekeepers for the modern day woman
column17: this Sona Sitara series watch from Sonata instils in its wearer a sense of poise and grace while also giving great flaunt value. A perfect accessory to flaunt on dressy occasions
column18: this chic timepiece gels perfectly with any of the multitude of dresses that you have gathered over time in your wardrobe. Wear this beautiful analog watch and win the hearts of men at any party or social event; accessorised with the right clothes
column19:
this watch will transform you into a diva.

Body & Design

\r\n\tThis specialised women\u2019s timepiece features a very contemporary dial that is crafted with precision and is an epitome of elegance. This highly creative and innovative dial is designed to fit in a diagonal form rather than your standard round or box dials. The inside of the dial features a watch face that has a smooth design with serene colours. The watch features only four digit markers which are indicated by carefully placed individual crystals in the 12
column22:
and 9 o\u2019clock positions.

\r\n\tThe all-important metal strap on this watch follows the basic form and contour of the dial and goes all the way around
column23: which keeps this highly fashionable watch firmly attached to your wrist at all times. The first strap link on either side of the dial features an extensive arrangement of eye-catching crystals
column24:
making it as much of a fashion accessory as it is a personal timekeeper.
\r\n\t\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0
Functions and Other Features

\r\n\tThe stylish look of the fashionable timepiece is complemented by its superlative performance. Designed to resist water up to a depth of 30 m
column25: this Sonata watch is enabled to withstand minimal splashing of water. You can let go of your fears while wearing this watch before stepping out of your house during the monsoon. Contemporary and fashionable
column26:
this Sonata analog watch for women is a perfect accessory for the new-age women who define their existence through their poise.

\n

Key Features

  • Water Resistant
  • Red Strap

Sleek
column17: smooth and sophisticated
column18: this wonderfully designed analog watch from Sonata\u2019s Yuva Gold collection for women comes well equipped to accurately keep track of time and do so with great style. Presenting a prominent design that is all about expressing grace and elegance
column19:
this women’s watch is a definite choice for any of your casual get-togethers.

Body and Design

The Sonata Yuva Gold Analog Watch sports a contemporary dial that houses an attractively coloured watch face. The dial’s background has a subtle pattern so as to eliminate any sense of monotony. As part of the distinctive design
column20: the dial on this women\u2019s analog watch features only six hour markers which are on the 3
column21: 4 and 5-hour positions on the right and the 9
column22: 10 and 11-hour positions on the left side of the dial. These hour markers along with the watch\u2019s three time indicating hands have a sophisticated metallic finish
column23:
which against the deep colour of the watch face provides for easy and trouble-free time reading.

The stylish and contemporary dial on this Sonata Yuva Gold watch is enveloped in a sturdy case with the same metallic finish as the watch hands and the hour markers. This case not only adds to the watch’s high aesthetic value but also provides the all-important dial with a much needed level of durability and protection.

Functions and Other Features

All the changes and adjustments that you wish to make to the positions of the watch hands can easily be accomplished with the rotating crown located on the right side of the dial’s case. This metallic case has extensions at the top and bottom portions forming lugs that serve the purpose of attaching it to the watch’s extremely attractive leather strap. The leather strap helps keep this Yuva Gold analog watch from Sonata comfortably attached to your wrist as long as your need. The dial’s sturdy case combines with a hardy clear glass cover to give the watch the ability to be water-resistant up to a depth of 30 m.

Boasting a high level of aesthetics
column24: functionality and durability
column25: this personal timekeeper from Sonata\u2019s Yuva Gold series gives its wearer a highly improved sense of style and sophistication
column26:
while also providing great flaunt value.

column12:
'desc': [u'

Sonata Yuva Analog Watch - For Women (Pink) Price: Rs.765

Key Features

  • Round Dial
  • Pink Strap
  • Water Resistant

If a man calls you girly for liking pretty pink clothes
column14: you should take it as a compliment. To celebrate everything that is delicate and every so endearing about women Sonata presents a lovely analog watch\xa0from the Yuva Series that resonates with feminine charm. This elegant watch is for the woman who is unabashed by her femininity and does not pretend to be a gearhead to please others. Her innocence is her greatest asset and the Sonata Yuva watch\xa0is an accessory that matches her personality and her wardrobe. The Sonata Yuva watch goes well with your casual kurtis
column15:
jeans and even your pretty summer dresses. So dress up all you want and feel prettier than ever because you deserve it.\xa0

Body and Design

The soft toned round dial is beautified with slim time markers in Roman numerals. The bezel and case of the watch have been studded with clear stones only to harp on the old saying that diamonds are a girl’s best friends and rightfully so. The stones have been carefully placed to give the give the watch depth
column16:
but without overdoing it. To hold the lovely timepiece elegantly on your wrist is a leather strap with tonal stitching. The leather strap is soft on your skin and makes the watch comfortable to wear all day.

Functions and Other Features

If there is one scene from Bollywood movies that every girl indisputably loves it’s when the heroine runs out into the rain to do that splendid rain dance. You can go ahead do your own version of the rain dance on the spur of a moment and nothing can hold you back from it
column17:
not even your pretty watch because the Yuva watch is water resistant up to 30 m making it splash-and rain-resistant.

The Sonata Yuva Analog watch is the true essence of femininity and gives you a beautiful accessory to pair with your clothes. You don’t have to play videogames or drive fast cars to be noticed because all you need is the charming innocence that makes you beautiful and the Sonata Yuva Analog Watch adds to your innate beauty.

']

column14:
'desc': [u'

Sonata Bracelet Analog Watch - For Women (Gold) Price: Rs.1315

Key Features

  • Oval Dial
  • Golden Strap
  • Water Resistant

Slim
column16: this wonderfully designed watch is from Sonata. An analog watch from the Bracelet collection for women
column17:
this chic timepiece comes well equipped to accurately keep track of time and also do so with great elegance and style. This is an ideal accessory to sport on dressy occasions; the graceful timepiece will blend in with any attire that you have stacked up in your wardrobe over time. Wear this watch to a party and mesmerise other guests with the infallible charm of this graceful time wear.

Body & Design

The ultra-chic design that this Sonata analog wristwatch is built around finds its origin at the watch’s impressively crafted oval shaped dial
column18: which sports a very plain and uncluttered light coloured background. The seconds and the hour hand are given a rich metallic finish
column19:
while the minutes hand and most of the digit markers are given a rich contrasting colour against the light background. This clever use of colours not only enhances the aesthetic value of the watch but also makes it extremely easy to tell the time with just a simple glance at the dial.

The Sonata Bracelet watch for women is kept firmly and comfortably attached to your wrist at all times with the help of a plush metal strap which also carries the same colour as the dial’s digit markings and the watch hands. The unique shape of the strap adds a glamorous touch to this fashionable time wear. The comfy strap will make sure that you do not feel discomfited even after prolonged use of the chic timepiece.

Functions and Other Features

Monsoon always arrives unannounced. A few spells of unanticipated shower can leave you drenched to the core. However
column20: a few splashes of water will not affect the functioning of this superb time wear because this watch is water resistant up to a depth of 30 m. Thus
column21:
with this Sonata watch you can enjoy efficient functionality along with dazzling looks. The sheer grace and sophistication that this women\u2019s analog Sonata wristwatch expresses make it an ideal choice for any social gatherings or even a formal black-tie or a red carpet event.

\n
\n ']

column16:
'desc': [u'

Maxima Analog Watch - For Women (White) Price: Rs.845

Key Features

  • Rectangular Dial
  • White Strap
  • Water Resistant
  • Buckle Clasp

Watches are the perfect way to complement the clothes you wear. Are you looking for a simple and elegant watch that can stand up to the demands of daily use
column17: yet be stylish enough to wear on those classy evenings out? Perhaps
column18: you think of a watch as an accessory and aim to add a few more to that collection of yours. Whatever the need may be
column19:
the Maxima analog watch for women seems to be the appropriate choice. This casual watch from Maxima sports a classy analog dial driven by a battery powered quartz mechanism that keeps both you and the watch ticking right through the day.\xa0

Body and Design

The analog watch from Maxima comes with a leather strap. The leather strap makes this watch very comfortable to wear over long periods of time. The watch also features a rectangular dial that is encased in a steel bezel. The simplistic design of the rectangular dial
column20: with its three display hands
column21:
really accentuates the beauty of such a watch.

Functions and Other Features

\r\n

\r\n\tThe women\'s analog watch from Maxima is designed to be water resistant as well as water resistant to a depth of 30 m
column22:
making your next trip to one of those scenic waterfalls even more enjoyable.

\xa0

column16:
'desc': [u'

Maxima Ssteele Analog Watch - For Women (White) Price: Rs.1695

Key Features

  • Rectangular Dial
  • White Strap
  • Water Resistant

The elegantly-designed watches from the Ssteele collection of Maxima will impress any urbane fashionista. The regal timepieces have an impeccable charm that will impress the stylish woman in you. The chic craftsmanship and the technical finesse of the Ssteele series of watches will satisfy the needs of the connoisseurs for timepieces.

This Maxima Ssteele Analog Watch for women will make a long-lasting impression in the heart of any onlooker. Crafted with brilliance
column17:
the regal watch suits any casual attire that graces your wardrobe. Wear the watch for a casual meet up with friends or for a light shopping spree; you will look your ravishing best.

Body and Design

The Maxima watch from the Ssteele series comes with a rectangular dial that is enclosed within a case with an unusual shape. The light-coloured dial is surrounded by a crystal-studded bezel
column18: making it pleasing to the eyes. Moreover
column19: the vibrant colour of the seconds hand as well as the 12th hour marker accentuates the glamorous appeal of the timepiece. The analog women\'s watch from Maxima also sports a comfy leather strap
column20: contributing to the overall aesthetics of the watch. Thanks to the presence of the leather strap
column21: you will not feel the slightest discomfort
column22:
no matter how long you wear the watch. The stitched borders and the fine texture of the strap will elevate your fashion quotient.

Functions and Other Features

The Maxima analog watch for women is designed to be water-resistant
column23: so
column24: venturing out of home on a rainy day to catch a live music concert should no longer be a problem. The water-resistance feature enables you to jump right into the pool at a water theme park
column25: without worrying about the safety of your watch. A unique watch for the fashion conscious women
column26:
this dainty women\u2019s analog timepiece from Maxima will boost your style quotient.

When you are looking for a watch that would function as a daily wear accessory
column17: at the top most of your list of features or attributes you would like a watch to have are probably comfort
column18: reliability and functionality. This watch from Standard series of Casio aims to meet just those criteria. The analog watch from Casio is designed for women who like their accessories to be both stylish
column19: while yet at the same time not compromising on comfort
column20: when they wear them through the week. The watch features a battery powered quartz mechanism to help perfectly sync the time displayed on the dial
column21:
to the time zone you are aligned to.

Body and Design

The trendy women’s watch from the Standard series of Casio sports a rectangular dial that should accentuate all the formal wear in your wardrobe
column22: extremely well. To protect this dial from jolts
column23: spills and corrosive elements in the air
column24:
the Casio women\u2019s analog watch features a stainless steel case.

\r\n\tTo ensure that Casio watch from the Standard line remains comfortable no matter how long it is fastened to your wrist
column25:
the watch features a 11 mm wide stainless steel strap. Stainless steel as a material is especially durable against moisture making it quite capable of handling any perspiration in might encounter during the day.

Functions and Other Features

The women’s Standard series watch from Casio is equipped to be water resistant. This water resistant feature proves to be particularly useful when it comes to protecting the insides of the watch from the humidity of coastal areas or the rains during the monsoon. The watch is also equipped to be water resistant up to a depth of 30 m
column26:
making it the perfect accessory you would take to the pool on those relaxing Sunday afternoon swims.

The Casio Standard analog watch for women is just the watch to draw attention to the formal attire your wear to work during the week as well as to highlight the blue denims and colourful t-shirt look you usually go for over the weekend.

  • Water Resistant
  • Stainless Steel Case
  • Contemporary Dial
  • White Strap

This trendy watch for women is a product from the stables of Q&Q. The women’s watch is branded as a casual wear accessory that
column17: when the need presents itself
column18: can step up to being a party wear accessory as well. The analog Q&Q watch makes use of a battery powered quartz mechanism to keep the device ticking in perfect sync with your time zone. A quartz mechanism is a sure-fire
column19: as well as cost-effective
column20: way of knowing that you\u2019re timepiece will accurately adhere to international time keeping standards
column21:
no matter what.

Body and Design

To ensure the wearer with the utmost comfort while she sports the analog women’s Q&Q watch the designers of the elegant timepiece have equipped it with a soft leather strap. This leather strap is designed to fit snugly around the contours of your wrist for hours on end
column22:
while you work hard at office or carry out your daily chores at home.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe Q&Q watch for women is designed around a stainless steel case. This stainless steel case makes certain\xa0that the integral inner workings of the timepiece are not affected
column23: if and when the wristwatch is inadvertently dropped or otherwise mishandled. Moreover
column24:
it is this case that protects the intricately designed contemporary shaped dial.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe dial on the analog women\u2019s Q&Q watch
column25: with its three watch hands
column26: is accentuated by the ornamented bezel and bold index hour markers. These two features combine to make reading the time on the Q&Q watch very legible and even to some extent
column27:
delightful. This dial makes use of a mineral glass window to ensure that even the most determined of scratches do not find the their way on to the dial.

Functions and Other Features

The women’s analog watch from Q&Q is designed to be waterproof from minimal splashing. This water-resistant feature makes certain that timepiece keeps ticking
column28: even when your garden sprinkles switch on while you attempt to cover the distance between the sidewalk and main door. The women\u2019s Q&Q watch
column29: with its eloquent design and unmistakeable charm
column30:
proves to be the ideal accessory to adorn when you leave home.

\r\n\tAs a glittering symbol of great craftsmanship and heightened aesthetics is this beautifully conceived timepiece from Q&Q\u2019s highly desirable line of women\u2019s analog watches. An ideal choice of personal timekeepers for the trendy and fashion conscious woman
column18: this analog watch from Q&Q accentuates in its wearer a sense of beauty and elegance
column19:
making it an automatic selection for all your casual events or parties.

Body and Design

The incredibly trendy women’s wristwatch from Q&Q features a fashionable rectangular dial that houses an attractive yet mellow background colour. This plain and solid coloured background features a metallic coloured design to disrupt the monotony of the watch face. The outermost track on the watch face carries the dial’s timekeeping markings in a dark colour; while the three watch hands carry a bright metallic colour. This clever use of different colours on the watch face
column20:
especially against such a light colour give you great dial visibility for easy time reading.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis highly creative and beautifully put together dial is surrounded by a thick alloy case that is designed to provide the dial with an improved level of durability and damage resistance. An alloy is a mixture that is composed of two or more metals
column21:
which in this case is aimed at producing a metal alloy that stronger and lighter than the original metal elements. This highly specialized alloy case while protecting the dial also contributes to the watch’s aesthetic value with its bright metallic finish which is encrusted with an array of stones or crystals.

The top and bottom portions of the bright metallic stone-studded alloy case have provision which allows the case to be attached to the watch’s classy and sensual leather strap that carries the same colour as the watch face. This stylish leather strap is wholly responsible for keeping this exquisite women’s personal timepiece comfortably perched to your wrist as long as you desire.

The dial on this Q&Q women’s analog watch is give a significant amount of protection in the form of a clear curved glass. All the time related changes or alterations on the dial can easily be made using the watch’s rotating screw crown found on the right side of the dial’s alloy case. The combination of the dial’s alloy case along with the curved glass cover gives the dial a substantial water-resistant ability. This high durability with water-resistance makes sure that the watch is more than capable of brushing off that occasional drop or that unexpected spray of water that is headed your way.

Together
column22: with a\xa0<strong>rich colour

    • Life would be a sad old picture if we didn’t add a little colour to it and the Q&Q Analog watch has been designed to brighten up your day with a splash of colour. This vibrant sports watch is for the woman who is upbeat and takes life in her stride. The watch can go with your denim skirts and T-shirts and would even look stunning when you wear a suit and trousers.

    The colourful Q&Q analog watch not only adds spunk to your style but also proves to be a resilient watch that is meant to back the tough cookie that you are. Whether you enjoy basketball on weekends or want to sit back and sip coffee with friends
column18:
the watch adds to your style and stays put when you are out on your daily adventures. The impeccable precision of the quartz mechanism ensures that the watch is running in time and so are you.

Body and Design

The striking round dial is flanked with bold time markers and 3 equally stunning time display hands. On the bezel of the watch you will find clear 10-second markers in numerals. The watch comes together with the bright and vibrant plastic strap. The use of plastic makes the watch durable and resistant to wear and tear. The plastic strap is comfortable on the skin and allows you to wear the watch for long periods of time.

Functions and Other Features

If you are someone who likes helping your mom out in their garden and don’t mind digging your hands into the dirt then the Q&Q watch is just right for you. The watch is protected with a mineral glass dial cover that keeps the watch safe from scratches. And even if you get a little dirt on the watch you can simply give it a thorough wash because the watch is water resistant up to a depth of 50 m. The plastic strap doesn’t get wet and can simply be wiped down to clean it.

Once you are done helping mom out you can head straight out to meet your friends at the beach. The snazzy sports watch is sure to match your ever so awesome swim wear so
column19: whether you choose to play volleyball on the beach or take a swim in sea
column20:
you look great with this dapper accessory. The Q&Q also features the very handy date display so you don’t have to fumble about with your phone to know what the date is.

This youthful watch from Q&Q is for the woman who is active and adventurous and needs a watch that can keep up with her busy and bustling life.

column12:
'desc': [u'

Sonata Yuva Analog Watch - For Women (Pink) Price: Rs.765

Key Features

  • Round Dial
  • Pink Strap
  • Water Resistant

If a man calls you girly for liking pretty pink clothes
column14: you should take it as a compliment. To celebrate everything that is delicate and every so endearing about women Sonata presents a lovely analog watch\xa0from the Yuva Series that resonates with feminine charm. This elegant watch is for the woman who is unabashed by her femininity and does not pretend to be a gearhead to please others. Her innocence is her greatest asset and the Sonata Yuva watch\xa0is an accessory that matches her personality and her wardrobe. The Sonata Yuva watch goes well with your casual kurtis
column15:
jeans and even your pretty summer dresses. So dress up all you want and feel prettier than ever because you deserve it.\xa0

Body and Design

The soft toned round dial is beautified with slim time markers in Roman numerals. The bezel and case of the watch have been studded with clear stones only to harp on the old saying that diamonds are a girl’s best friends and rightfully so. The stones have been carefully placed to give the give the watch depth
column16:
but without overdoing it. To hold the lovely timepiece elegantly on your wrist is a leather strap with tonal stitching. The leather strap is soft on your skin and makes the watch comfortable to wear all day.

Functions and Other Features

If there is one scene from Bollywood movies that every girl indisputably loves it’s when the heroine runs out into the rain to do that splendid rain dance. You can go ahead do your own version of the rain dance on the spur of a moment and nothing can hold you back from it
column17:
not even your pretty watch because the Yuva watch is water resistant up to 30 m making it splash-and rain-resistant.

The Sonata Yuva Analog watch is the true essence of femininity and gives you a beautiful accessory to pair with your clothes. You don’t have to play videogames or drive fast cars to be noticed because all you need is the charming innocence that makes you beautiful and the Sonata Yuva Analog Watch adds to your innate beauty.
